305
00:18:10,484 --> 00:18:11,405
(Do you know that Yunsheng)

306
00:18:11,405 --> 00:18:13,244
(turned the opportunity abroad
down because of you?)

307
00:18:14,084 --> 00:18:15,645
You'd rather ruin his future

308
00:18:15,925 --> 00:18:17,324
