I see.

344
00:20:37,685 --> 00:20:41,044
You never intended to help me
from the start.

345
00:20:42,405 --> 00:20:44,244
You were just using me all along, right?

346
00:20:44,804 --> 00:20:47,484
Miss Tian, we are all adults,

347
00:20:48,524 --> 00:20:50,484
